<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang = "pt-BR">

<head>
    <meta charset = "UTF-8">
    <meta name    = "viewport" content = "width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Novo Agendamento Criado</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Red+Hat+Display:wght@400;500;700&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family     : "Red Hat Display", sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin          : 0;
            padding         : 0;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width       : 600px;
            margin          : 50px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding         : 30px;
            border-radius   : 12px;
            border          : 1px solid #ddd;
            box-shadow      : 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color           : #ffffff;
            text-align      : center;
            background-color: #f87fc4;
            padding         : 15px;
            border-radius   : 12px 12px 0 0;
            font-size       : 24px;
            font-weight     : 700;
            margin          : 0;
        }

        p {
            color      : #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin     : 15px 0;
            font-size  : 16px;
        }

        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin    : 30px 0;
        }

        a.button {
            display         : inline-block;
            padding         : 15px 35px;
            background-color: #fd9323;
            color           : white;
            text-decoration : none;
            border-radius   : 6px;
            font-size       : 18px;
            font-weight     : bold;
        }

        a.button:hover {
            background-color: #ffa54d;
            transition      : background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .agendamento-container {
            display        : flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap            : 20px;
            margin-top     : 20px;
        }

        .agendamento-antigo,
        .agendamento-novo {
            width           : 48%;
            padding         : 10px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius   : 8px;
            box-shadow      : 0px 0px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            color     : #999;
            font-size : 12px;
        }

        .footer img {
            width        : 150px;
            height       : auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class = "email-container">
        <h1>Novo Agendamento Criado</h1>

        <p>Olá {{admin.nome}}, </p>
        <p>Um novo agendamento foi criado: </p>
        
            <p><strong>Serviço     : </strong> {{event.title}}</p>
            <p><strong>Data        : </strong> {{event.start}}</p>
            <p><strong>Horário     : </strong> {{event.hora}}</p>
            <p><strong>Profissional: </strong> {{event.professionalName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Usuário     : </strong> {{user.nome}}</p>
        

        <p>Se você tiver alguma dúvida, entre em contato conosco.</p>
        <p>Atenciosamente,<br>A Equipe PattyNails ♡</p>
        
        <div class = "footer">
        <a   href  = "http://localhost:3003/">
        <img src   = "cid:logoPattyNails" alt = "Logo PattyNails">
            </a>
            <p>© 2024 PattyNails</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
